data.description: Welcome to your dream property! This spacious home boasts an oversized lot that provides ample space for all your needs. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast with a boat and RV or an entrepreneur looking for a space to operate your business, this property has you covered.     Key Features:  New Roof: Enjoy peace of mind with a brand-new roof that provides protection for years to come.  Updated A/C: Stay cool and comfortable year-round with a state-of-the-art air conditioning system.  Updated Water Heater: Never run out of hot water with a recently installed water heater.  Double Pane Windows: Experience energy efficiency and noise reduction with upgraded windows.  French Doors: Elegant French doors add a touch of sophistication to your home.  Terrazzo and Tile Floors: Stylish and easy-to-maintain flooring throughout the house.  Fenced-In Property: Privacy and security are guaranteed with a fully fenced-in yard.  Above Ground Pool: Dive into relaxation and fun in your very own above-ground pool.  Spa: Unwind and rejuvenate in your private spa, creating the ultimate in relaxation.  Patio: Entertain guests or simply unwind on the spacious patio area.  Landscaping: Beautifully landscaped surroundings create a serene atmosphere.  Dog Run: A dedicated space for your furry friends to play and exercise.  Pergola: Enjoy outdoor gatherings and shade under the charming pergola.  Covered RV/Boat Parking: Protect your recreational vehicles from the elements with a covered parking area.  Shed: Additional storage space for all your tools and equipment.  Carport: Convenient covered parking for your vehicles.    This property offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and versatility. With its extensive features and spacious lot, it's an ideal place to call home while accommodating your business and recreational needs. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity!
